This was supposedly fixed by r15927. But since the commented code was resurrected in r16328 this bug is reappearing. 

Here's a simple example:

{code}
trait Test {
 def testFunc(i:Int) = ((i:Int) => i + 5)(i)
}
{code}

And here the console session:

{code}
